d still broken so he was done with the car.  Turns out the repair shop didnt flush out the radiator.  So the tranny overheated and fried up.  I flushed out the tranny and i had no third.  So i drove around without a 3rd gear.  I didnt go on the highway. After a while i lost 2nd. So it sat. I ended up giving it to my little brother.  He swapped out the fried tranny for another one. I forgot what kind, but i know the kickdown cable linkage didnt work. So now he enjoyed the XR.  He lost the rear end due to bald tires. And ended up crashing into a van. The car wasnt that bad. Thanks to that big bumper.  So the car sat again.  Fixed the body work. so he decided to fix it up. He added a throttle body off of a 4.6 V8. got rid of the cat.  but he moved to Texas and didnt have enough time to finish nor money to move it. So now its back in my hands again. Im added an intercooler off of a 89 probe 2.2. So now I need hi-temp hoses for it. I also need the cooling pipes that run along the head on the turbo side. Its 2 pipes. heater,turbo, and res. tank. Any help?<br>
